    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Baptiste alternates between damage and healing rounds on Biotic Launcher, dropping Immortality Field to prevent a wipe and Exo Boots to reposition to a safer angle.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Immortality Field is a single fixed point that enemies can play around or bait out early, and once it's down he has no other answer to a follow-up burst combo.</p>"
